### Refresh ADMIN (используем refreshToken из логина ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbkB0ZXN0LmNvbSIsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MjY0NDU1MywiZXhwIjoxNzgzMjQ5MzUzfQ.9KJKxFBJVsH4LvHJKB0zbGqCoUYSA4oQYxwAYWM6FqM"
}

### Logout ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbkB0ZXN0LmNvbSIsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MjY0NDU1MywiZXhwIjoxNzgzMjQ5MzUzfQ.9KJKxFBJVsH4LvHJKB0zbGqCoUYSA4oQYxwAYWM6FqM"
